    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "b32e5bf3-2075-4261-b3ee-9b55355cbbc9",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "When You Wish Upon A Waterlily",
        "Location": "LOCATION_HOKKAIDO_FLU",
        "PublicId": "118393716240",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Hokkaido/_scene_flu.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5561ba7b-91a6-4403-a351-227015f67c2f).Image",
        "Description": "After the Liebleid incident, Jeff has been enjoying the utilities provided at GAMA.\r\rHe took up an origami class to fuel a creative outlet since the death of his cherished girlfriend Rebecca. His motif of her was symbolized as a multitude of small waterlily models, of which he was later bullied by his fellow classmates for.\r\rJeff has decided he doesn&apos;t want to die because his origami journey isn&apos;t finished, however he did decide his fellow classmates&apos; journeys have.\r\rDo what you must. Good luck.",
